            "descriptionRaw": "Leaving a single Ice Lotus behind, Ganyu dashes backward, shunning all impurity and dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>AoE Cryo DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Ice Lotus</color>\n·Continuously taunts surrounding opponents, attracting them to attack it.\n·Endurance scales based on Ganyu's Max HP.\n·Blooms profusely when destroyed or once its duration ends, dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>AoE Cryo DMG</color>.\n\n<i>\"You saw me, you say? You must be mistaken. I was working overtime then.\"</i>",
            "name": "Trail of the Qilin"
        },
