            "descriptionRaw": "Coalesces atmospheric frost and snow to summon a Sacred Cryo Pearl that exorcises evil.\nDuring its ability duration, the Sacred Cryo Pearl will continuously rain down shards of ice, striking opponents within an AoE and dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>Cryo DMG</color>.\n\n<i>Ganyu can bring down sweet rains as a matter of course. But against demons and heretics, they become bitter, freezing snow.</i>",
            "name": "Celestial Shower"
        },
